27:17.303 --> 27:19.069
[Elise screams]

27:19.071 --> 27:22.740
[camera shuttering]

27:22.742 --> 27:24.775
Give me that!

27:24.777 --> 27:25.909
[Paparazzi]
     Whoa, whoa. Hey, hey.

27:25.911 --> 27:27.011
[Elise upset] Argh!

27:31.917 --> 27:34.785
[taxi driver] All right buddy.
 So what's up? Where we going?

28:09.121 --> 28:12.456
Hey look, this is the last time
   I'm gonna answer my phone
Billy, so you know make it good.

28:12.792 --> 28:13.857
Ryan, where are you?

28:15.327 --> 28:17.294
Oh, you know Billy,
        someplace warm.

28:17.296 --> 28:20.964
So am I.
       It's called Hell!

28:20.966 --> 28:22.866
What are you thinking?
     You can't just leave.

28:22.868 --> 28:25.869
Ryan,
  we have major problems here.

28:25.871 --> 28:29.206
That DUI put you in breach of
 contract, you understand that?

28:29.341 --> 28:32.209
That means Lang's not obligated
       to pay you a dime

28:32.211 --> 28:34.244
while you're injured, and now
    he's even talking about

28:34.246 --> 28:38.415
canceling your contract
   altogether, and suing you!

28:38.784 --> 28:42.286
This is most definitely not the
 time to be taking a vacation!

28:45.124 --> 28:48.358
[Billy on phone]
         Hello? Hello?

28:51.363 --> 28:53.731
He hung up.

28:53.733 --> 28:56.200
[sighs]

28:56.202 --> 28:57.801
Don't stop.

29:00.406 --> 29:05.109
Oh my god, Lana.
      I snuck a picture of
    him going into his room.

29:05.111 --> 29:08.212
He is perfection!

29:09.482 --> 29:14.017
I would do things to him that
 are illegal in most countries.

29:14.019 --> 29:16.386
Girls, he's engaged!

29:16.388 --> 29:20.324
[Amanda clears throat]
    TMZ said they broke up,

29:20.326 --> 29:23.026
and she isn't here, but I am.

29:23.028 --> 29:25.496
If Zimmer even catches
you flirting, you'll get fired.

29:25.498 --> 29:28.766
Zimmer's got to catch me first.

29:28.768 --> 29:31.235
I'm gonna harpoon that whale.

29:39.545 --> 29:41.078
Good evening.

29:41.080 --> 29:44.982
Uh... Lana?

29:44.984 --> 29:46.950
I'm Ryan.
       Nice to meet you.

29:46.952 --> 29:48.352
Ryan Hawkes?

29:48.854 --> 29:52.289
Oh, goddamnit. Was there
   like a memo or something?

29:52.291 --> 29:54.858
Actually, there was.

29:55.528 --> 29:56.794
Right.

29:57.096 --> 29:59.963
Um, What can I get you, sir?

29:59.965 --> 30:03.200
Umm, okay.
      First two things...

30:03.202 --> 30:08.505
don't call me sir,
    and uh second, um, dirty
     martini. Upside down.

30:08.507 --> 30:10.307
Coming right up.

30:22.888 --> 30:25.022
Very good.
It's good. Very good.

30:25.024 --> 30:26.857
[piano player]
    Thanks. Goodnight Lana.

30:26.859 --> 30:28.992
-[Hawkes] Goodnight!
       -[Lana] Bye, Sam.

30:32.097 --> 30:34.965
Oh, we closed this place down.

30:35.968 --> 30:38.335
So, Lana, Lana. Talk to me.

30:38.337 --> 30:41.605
Um, I wanna know things.
        Where you from?

30:41.607 --> 30:43.941
You from Russia?

30:43.943 --> 30:46.260
St. Petersburg.

30:46.261 --> 30:48.578
St. Petersburg?
   Like Zenit St. Petersburg?
          That's cool.

30:48.581 --> 30:49.913
Pretty cool.

30:49.915 --> 30:51.415
Is that all you know
         about Russia?

30:51.417 --> 30:53.951
[Hawkes scoffs]
             No...

30:53.953 --> 30:57.955
There's Sputnik,
   and it snows all the time.

30:57.957 --> 31:03.327
There's giant um,
       bears everywhere.

31:03.329 --> 31:06.430
Yeah. I keep one as a pet.

31:08.234 --> 31:11.102
You know you don't.

31:11.103 --> 31:13.971
Um, I'm, I'm getting
   the feeling that you don't
    really wanna talk to me.

31:13.973 --> 31:19.910
Okay, Mr. Talker.
      So, what brings you
        to this cruise?

31:19.912 --> 31:24.448
Maybe I just uh, just
      came here to drown.

31:24.450 --> 31:26.650
Just know in case there
        is an accident,

31:26.652 --> 31:31.388
and the ship starts sinking,
   we are the ones who'll be
     manning the lifeboats.

31:31.390 --> 31:34.324
You will manage a lifeboat?
         The whole one?

31:34.326 --> 31:38.428
Mm-hmm. It's my job,
 to save people from drowning.

31:40.566 --> 31:43.567
Of course, except...
           I'm sorry.

31:43.569 --> 31:45.636
Is it me or is this
         ship spinning?

31:45.638 --> 31:49.406
I'm pretty sure it's you.
  And you should go to sleep.

31:49.408 --> 31:55.112
All right, fine.
 Because I like you, I'm gonna
      go, but I'm gonna...

31:55.114 --> 31:57.214
I'm, excuse me,
       I'm gonna see you.

31:57.216 --> 31:59.182
I'm gonna see you...

31:59.184 --> 31:59.917
Soon.

31:59.919 --> 32:01.018
Hm?

32:02.288 --> 32:05.489
