             right?

43:51.663 --> 43:53.163
Well, their month.

43:53.164 --> 43:54.664
Good enough. All right,
let's do it. Come on, kids.

43:54.666 --> 43:56.149
Let's go, come on, guys.

43:56.150 --> 43:57.633
Let's play, let's play.
    Let's go, come on, run!

44:03.008 --> 44:04.707
[Hawkes]
     All right, go, go, go!

44:26.331 --> 44:31.434
