          Yeah, yeah!

44:34.773 --> 44:39.375
Oh man. I tell you one thing,
      it's not fixed yet.

44:39.377 --> 44:44.847
-[Hawkes] But uh, you're right.
  -[Lana] It's gonna be fine.
       You'll get there.

44:52.357 --> 44:53.289
[Hawkes laughs]

44:53.291 --> 44:54.891
[Lana] Sorry, no ice.

44:54.893 --> 44:58.428
No, you're a lifesaver. Thank
    you. Oh, so much better.

45:01.800 --> 45:04.333
Ryan, that's a great thing you
did back there.

45:04.335 --> 45:05.852
Stop it.

45:05.853 --> 45:07.370
It was very cool.

45:07.372 --> 45:08.571
I'll tell you something,

45:08.572 --> 45:09.771
I haven't had that much fun
            playing

45:09.774 --> 45:10.940
since I don't know when.

45:13.878 --> 45:14.944
We should do more of that.

