Plays for fun.
     Ryan, you're his hero.

46:33.158 --> 46:34.157
Poor guy.

46:34.159 --> 46:37.493
[Hawkes] Ryan... Hawkes.

46:39.831 --> 46:41.864
Give that to Danny, and uh...

46:41.866 --> 46:43.299
How do you know him?

46:44.135 --> 46:46.903
Um... Actually, Danny is um...

